Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=18}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:02.19,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{This bites... My body... is on fire.-OG}Que droga...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:04.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{This bites... My body... is on fire.-OG}Meu corpo... está queimando.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.24,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{So I'm still alive.-OG}Acho que... ainda estou vivo.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:11.99,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I wonder if I'll die like this...-OG}Mas... por quanto tempo mais...?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.67,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see no one on board.-OG}Não tem ninguém aqui.{Chloe}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.92,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Um navio abandonado, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.18,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Sucata de madeira... Sucata de ferro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:37.85,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{This place makes me... feel quite at home.-OG}Esse lugar me faz sentir... em casa.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:43.61,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have to do something \Nabout my disabled body first.-OG}Primeiro, preciso dar um jeito...\Nnesse corpo inútil!{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you know...-OG}Ficou sabendo?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:43.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that the violent \Ndisciple of Tom, Cutty Flam, died?-OG}O aprendiz violento do Tom, Cutty Flam, morreu.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:48.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele foi atropelado pelo sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Iceburg...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:54.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,você consegue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:58.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're the first disciple of Tom, \Nthe world's greatest shipwright.-OG}Tom era o maior carpinteiro do mundo,\Ne você era seu melhor aprendiz.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que você consegue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kokoro-san, let's drink \Ntogether one of these days...-OG}Dona Kokoro, vamos beber juntos\Num dia desses...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{when we have something to drink to.-OG}Pra relaxar um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.09,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san... - OG}Tom...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.26,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{please just watch.-OG}por favor, me observe.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.26,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll take over your will.-OG}Vou carregar a sua vontade.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.22,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll protect... everything!-OG}Vou proteger...{Chloe}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.18,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.19,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Esta cidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.48,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,e essas plantas também!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.36,Main-207+,,0,0,12,,{Iceburg-san, you have a guest. -OG}Iceburg, você tem uma visita.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He said you'd know who if I tell you "Cutty Flam."-OG}Ele disse que saberia quem é\Nse eu mencionasse "Cutty Flam".{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.03,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shall I show him in here?-OG}Devo mandá-lo entrar?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dispense-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:56.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a roundabout way of meeting.-OG}Que jeito complicado\Nde se encontrar.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:04:01.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... anyway, what's up \Nwith that funny looking body of yours?-OG}Bom... enfim, o que houve\Ncom esse corpo estranho?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up!-OG}Cala a boca!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:07.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since my whole body came to be of no use, I rebuilt my body using iron scraps and escaped death!-OG}Meu corpo estava destruído, então me reconstruí\Ncom sucata de metal pra sobreviver!{WF+AR}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais importante,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that your company contracts \Nto build ships for the World Government!-OG}ouvi que sua empresa está construindo\Nnavios pro Governo Mundial!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna tolerate you doing things \Nthat help the government!-OG}Não vou ficar calado enquanto\Nvocê ajuda aqueles desgraçados!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They took Tom san and...-OG}Depois que levaram o Tom e–{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And who made the weapons \Nthat caused the incident?!-OG}Esqueceu quem fez as armas\Nque {\i1}causaram{\i0} aquele incidente?!{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure you have things \Nyou wanna say to me,-OG}Tenho certeza que tem muita coisa\Nque quer me dizer...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:33.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but don't think for a second\NI've forgiven you after four years!-WF}mas não ache que te perdoei\Nnestes quatro anos.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm surprised that you had the nerve \Nto show your face after what happened!-OG}Depois do que aconteceu,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:37.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm surprised that you had the nerve \Nto show your face after what happened!-OG}não acredito que tem a cara de pau\Nde aparecer!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I completely thought that you were dead...-OG}Eu tinha certeza que você estava morto.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{since the government told me so.-OG}Foi o que o governo informou.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if Tom-san forgave you, \NI'm not going to forgive you!-OG}O Tom pode ter te perdoado,{Poppy+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if Tom-san forgave you, \NI'm not going to forgive you!-OG}mas eu nunca vou conseguir!{Poppy+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-Hey! What the hell are these?! Aren't these\Nthe blueprints we saw for that ancient weapon?!-OG}E-Ei, que diabos?!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:03.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-Hey! What the hell are these?! Aren't these\Nthe blueprints we saw for that ancient weapon?!-OG}Essas não são as plantas que vimos\Ndaquela arma ancestral?!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't use the name Cutty Flam from now on.-OG}Nunca mais use o nome Cutty Flam.{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The government couldn't \Nget this out of Tom-san.-OG}Como o governo não conseguiu\Ntirá-las do Tom,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's only a matter of time before I get targeted.-OG}é questão de tempo até\Nvirem atrás de mim.{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Leave the island with them... Franky.-OG}Leve-as e saia da ilha, Franky.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Leave this island?-OG}Sair da ilha?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cutty Flam da Tom's Workers está morto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:24.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As long as you don't use that name,\Nthere'll be no connection between us.-OG}Enquanto não usar esse nome,\Nnão podem nos conectar.{Poppy}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:29.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In addition, if you leave the island, the blueprints' whereabouts will vanish into the darkness.-OG}Saia da ilha com essas plantas\Ne o rastro delas desaparece de vez.{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:33.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-Hold on a sec! What happens if they come after you \Nwhen you don't have them?!-OG}E-Espera aí! E quando aparecerem\Ne você não tiver nada?!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've said what I came to say.-OG}Já disse o que tinha pra dizer.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Hey, Iceburg!-OG}Espera! Iceburg!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We may not see each other again.-OG}Talvez seja um adeus.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you want to end up like Tom-san?-OG}Quer acabar como o Tom?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fique com as plantas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If, by any chance, you find that your life \Nis in danger, just hand them over!-OG}Se sua vida estiver em perigo,\Né só entregar!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:54.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you don't wanna do that, then you \Ncan even burn them before their eyes!-OG}Se não quiser, queima elas\Nna cara deles!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você fosse eu, faria isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tom-san achieved so many great things,-OG}O Tom conquistou tanta coisa,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and he gave up everything in order \Nto preserve these blueprints for the future.-OG}e abriu mão de tudo\Npra proteger essas plantas.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:09.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At least, as long as there's a risk that a woman named Nico Robin can restore the weapon,-OG}Se há a menor chance de que Nico Robin\Npossa reviver a arma ancestral,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:13.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o mundo precisa dessas plantas pra revidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I continue to keep them with me...-OG}Mesmo que eu continue com elas...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{even if I am to be killed... \NI won't give them to the government!-OG}prefiro morrer... a entregar\Nas plantas pro governo!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you sure?-OG}Tem certeza?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I may build this weapon.-OG}Eu posso construir essa coisa.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it okay to trust me?-OG}Pode mesmo confiar em mim?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te entregar elas\Nnão responde essa pergunta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente nunca muda, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whenever we meet face to face, \Nwe yell at each other.-OG}Sempre que nos encontramos, gritamos um com o outro.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda não te perdoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and you may feel the same about me, too.-OG}e talvez você sinta o mesmo, mas...{WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,realmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{glad that... - OG}feliz...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que você esteja vivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! Stupid-burg! - OG}Espera, Iceburro!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:05.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna leave this island!-OG}Não vou sair desta ilha!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I do what I want! - OG}Eu faço o que eu quero!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jamais faria o que você manda,\Nnem que eu morra!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jamais!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You Moron-ky! Why don't \Nyou get what I'm saying?!-OG}Franburro idiota!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What we heard about Tom is \Nthat he had good skills,-OG}Ouvimos que Tom era um carpinteiro habilidoso,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:31.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but he was a ferocious and intractable fishman \Nwith superhuman strength.-OG}mas também um homem-peixe perigoso,\Nrebelde e com força monstruosa.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if we ask the townspeople, \Nthey just speak ambiguously.-OG}Quando perguntamos por aí, os moradores\Nsó deram respostas vagas.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must be tough to be a disciple that \Nhas to defend such a man, huh, Cutty Flam?-OG}Deve ser difícil como aprendiz\Ndefender um homem assim.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must be tough to be a disciple that \Nhas to defend such a man, huh, Cutty Flam?-OG}Não é, Cutty Flam?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not even worth responding to.-OG}Estou cansado demais pra morder essa isca.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're all crap!-OG}Vocês agentes do governo são um lixo!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Ei, ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:51.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At that time, more than 100 people, \Nincluding marines and officials,-OG}Naquela época, mais de 100 cidadãos,\Nincluindo fuzileiros e oficiais,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ficaram gravemente feridos aqui em Water 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O culpado foi você.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:01.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You had a lot to answer for, causing\Nthe World Government that much trouble,-OG}Você havia cometido um crime grave\Ncontra o Governo Mundial,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:05.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas como sua morte foi confirmada\Nno acidente do sea train naquele mesmo dia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{your charge was annulled.-OG}nenhuma acusação pôde ser feita.{AR}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:13.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, we'll take you \Nto Enies Lobby as a criminal.-OG}Mas agora, finalmente vamos levá-lo\Na Enies Lobby como criminoso.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can take your time there \Nanswering my question...-OG}Lá poderá responder com calma\Nàs nossas perguntas...{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{about the whereabouts of Pluton's blueprints.-WF}sobre o paradeiro das\Nplantas de Pluton.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Blueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É. Acabou de conectar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:35.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When I reported this case to our chief, he said he wanted to talk to you right away, so...-OG}Quando reportamos esse caso ao nosso chefe,\Nele quis falar com você imediatamente.{PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your chief? Hm?-OG}O chefe de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, prossiga, Chefe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's hot! It's hot! It's hot! I spilled the coffee!-OG}Tá quente! Tá quente! Tá quente! Derramei o café{\i0}!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:48.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Droga! Café idiota!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the hell?-OG}Que diab–{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vocês estão aí...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cutty Flam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I never thought you'd survived that...-OG}Nunca imaginei que tivesse sobrevivido...{WF+Chloe}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:07.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É difícil de acreditar, mas fico feliz em saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{During these past eight years... \Nevery time my scars hurt,-OG}Nestes oito anos,\Ntoda vez que minhas cicatrizes doíam,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:15.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was tormented by the rage\Nof knowing I could never get revenge...-WF}eu era atormentado por uma raiva\Nque não podia descontar em ninguém...{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:21.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{because the culprit who hurt me died!-OG}porque o criminoso\Nque me desfigurou tinha morrido.{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se lembra de mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:35.14,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,{I'm the man who was from Cipher Pol No. 5 and arrested Tom's Workers red-handed-OG}Sou o homem da Cipher Pol No. 5\Nque pessoalmente prendeu a Tom's Workers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:38.77,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,pelo ataque ao navio judicial há oito anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu maldito! Spanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"M"! You're missing the "M"! It's "Spandam"!-OG}Com "m"! É "Spandam", com "m"!{\i0}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estarei ansiosamente aguardando\Nsua chegada em Enies Lobby.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, guys!-OG}Agora, homens!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:57.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up \Nand bring that criminal here already!-OG}Parem de enrolar e tragam\Nesse criminoso logo!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ai! Tá quente! Tá quente! Tá quente!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lâmpada idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai, ai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! Let me go, you jerk!-OG}Droga! Me solta, seu idiota!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go.-OG}Vamos.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hold it, you bastards!-OG}Parados aí, seus desgraçados!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let him go!-OG}Soltem ele, agora!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah... I'm sorry.-OG}Minhas desculpas.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! You only shine for a second?!-OG}Ei! Essa pose é só de fachada?{Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I remember right, you are... \None of the Straw Hats, aren't you?-OG}Se não me engano, você é\Num dos Chapéus de Palha, certo?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não está funcionando! O vento é forte demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{The fire isn't going out at all!-OG}Não está apagando!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If people are still inside, \Nthey'll be done for if this keeps up!-OG}Quem estiver lá dentro\Nnão vai sobreviver assim!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san...! Paulie-san! - OG}Iceburg!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san...! Paulie-san!-OG}Paulie!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.12,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami... Oh, no...-OG}Nami...!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.25,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami... Oh, no...-OG}Isso é sério...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.92,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.25,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,tratá-la...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.59,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,agora... mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry! Give them treatment! \NThey've got terrible burns!-OG}Tratem eles imediatamente!\NAs queimaduras são graves!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! What're we gonna do with this reindeer?!-OG}Ei, e essa rena?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele também! Ele salvou a vida deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:55.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1939)}V-Verdade. Ei! Me dá uma mão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, boy...-OG}Puxa...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He got his butt whipped...-OG}Ele apanhou feio.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:11.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, resumindo, você não faz mais\Nparte dos Chapéus de Palha,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but you still haven't quit being a pirate, huh?-OG}mas ainda é um pirata safado, né?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're a pirate, then we'll take you.-OG}Nesse caso, vamos prender você também.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yep.-OG}Entendido.{Poppy}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And this ship...-OG}E esse navio...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You didn't take it down yet, huh?-OG}ainda não desmontou, né?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Don't you dare touch her!-OG}Ei! Não ouse encostar nela!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you doing?!-OG}Q-Que estão fazendo?!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Are you listening?!-OG}Ei, estão ouvindo?!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:51.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although it was an assumed identity, \Nwe are recognized shipwrights in this town.-OG}Mesmo que fossem fachada, somos carpinteiros\Nreconhecidos nesta cidade.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:13:00.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You should listen when we say \Nit's no good no matter what you do.-OG}Quando dizemos que um navio não presta,\Né melhor ouvir.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:06.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E daí?! Deixem ela em paz!\NEla nem é navio de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This will release the water, huh?-OG}Isso libera a água, certo?{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:12.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Não façam besteira! Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.97,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.89,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu carrego vocês por mais um tempinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Move back! It's gonna collapse!-OG}Afastem-se! Vai desabar!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You idiot! Run!-OG}Corre, idiota!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:31.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Não tem nada que possamos fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san has recovered consciousness!-OG}O Iceburg recuperou a consciência!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really?! That's great!-OG}Sério?! Que ótimo!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que alívio! Ele está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san!-OG}Iceburg!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É tudo graças àquela rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I heard that he's a pet of the Straw Hats.-OG}Mas... ouvi que ele é o pet dos Chapéus de Palha.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Essa aqui também!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A mulher acordou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:09.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What're we gonna do? Should we make her tell us \Nthe Straw Hats' whereabouts now?-OG}E-E agora? Devemos fazê-la\Nrevelar onde estão os Chapéus de Palha?{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But she's severely injured. \NAnd she's a woman, too.-OG}Parece estranho interrogar uma mulher ferida.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But that's...-OG}Mas–{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san! You shouldn't move around yet!-OG}Iceburg, você não devia se levantar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys...-OG}Pessoal...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{give us some space.-OG}nos deem espaço.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:27.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna talk to this woman alone.-OG}Quero falar com essa mulher a sós.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder what he wants \Nto talk alone with her about.-OG}Sobre o que será que estão conversando?{CPS, PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai! Por que fez isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem de ficar parados!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lucci-san and the others may still be inside!-OG}O Lucci e os outros podem ainda estar lá dentro!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos ajudem, seus idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's right. Hey!-OG}Ah, é verdade. Vamos!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Sorry!-OG}É, desculpa!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{First... I'm sorry.-OG}Primeiro, me desculpe.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We falsely accused you of the crime. I'll clear up the misunderstanding later.-OG}Acusamos vocês falsamente.\NVou esclarecer o mal-entendido depois.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna talk about Nico Robin.-OG}Quero falar sobre a Nico Robin.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sabe de alguma coisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did that woman change \Nafter you guys came to this town?-OG}Ela começou a agir estranho\Nquando chegaram a esta cidade?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, suddenly.-OG}Sim, foi muito repentino.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After she went out to town, \Nshe suddenly disappeared,-OG}Logo que chegamos à cidade,\Nela sumiu de repente.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:30.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and by this morning, she was\Nthe suspect of your attempted assassination.-OG}Nesta manhã, já era a principal\Nsuspeita da sua tentativa de assassinato.{PP+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When my friends finally found her,-OG}Quando nossa tripulação finalmente a encontrou...{WF+PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{she said she would no longer come back to us.-OG}ela disse que não voltaria mais.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We didn't know what was going on.-OG}Não entendíamos o que estava acontecendo,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:45.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So we came here tonight in order to ask her directly again\Nwhy she's leaving the ship.-OG}então viemos aqui essa noite pra perguntar\Nmais uma vez por que está saindo do navio.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.82,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra realizar meu desejo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:53.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{A wish that can never \Ncome true if I'm with you!-OG}Um desejo que nunca se realizará\Nse eu ficar com vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is this wish that can never \Ncome true if she's with us...?-OG}Qual é esse desejo que não pode\Nse realizar se ela ficar?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me tell you what I know.-OG}Vou contar o que sei.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:10.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi provavelmente quando vocês perderam\Na Nico Robin de vista pela primeira vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.68,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou com a CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A operação do governo\Njá estava em andamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há, claro, um motivo\Npara as ações daquela mulher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But before I tell you about that, - OG}Mas... antes de contar,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:30.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want you to know that Nico Robin and I both have a means to bring back the ancient weapon - OG}saiba que tanto Nico Robin quanto eu\Ntemos meios de reviver uma arma ancestral{WF/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que poderia destruir o mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Destruir o mundo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A problem occurred in our plan.-OG}{\i1}Nosso plano teve um imprevisto.{\i0}{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todos, venham ao quarto imediatamente.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não atirem no Iceburg ainda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, you get it, Nico Robin?-OG}Agora entendeu, Nico Robin?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As plantas que vocês queriam são falsas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:02.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if I am to be killed, I won't give those blueprints to the government!-OG}Mesmo que me matem, não entregarei\Nas plantas ao governo!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:08.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But if you're sniffing around\Nthe Poneglyphs on another front and helping the government as well,-OG}Mas se está fuçando nos poneglyphs\Ne ajudando o governo,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então tenho que te parar aqui e agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:18.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não estou buscando os poneglyphs\Npra reviver a arma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I just want to know the history, that's all.-OG}Eu só...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:20.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I just want to know the history, that's all.-OG}quero conhecer a história.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Such a claim doesn't mean anything!-OG}Isso não é desculpa!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:28.05,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu avisei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.21,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Várias e várias vezes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.68,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenha você a intenção ou não,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.35,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,armas não se importam com quem machucam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:41.73,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,mesmo que seja alguém que você ama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:47.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquilo que machuca as pessoas não\Nnecessariamente tem intenção maliciosa.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:53.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If that simple curiosity of wanting to know the history leads to the destruction of the world,-OG}Se sua simples curiosidade pela história\Ndo mundo levar à sua destruição,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you should die right here,\Nright now, Nico Robin!-OG}você deveria morrer aqui e agora, Nico Robin!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even after you saw the Ohara devils' fate, you still want to chase after the world's history?!-OG}{\q2}Ainda quer perseguir essa história depois de ver\No que aconteceu com aqueles demônios de Ohara?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't talk like you know \Neverything about Ohara!-OG}E o que {\i1}você{\i0} sabe sobre Ohara?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't even know...-OG}Você não faz ideia...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:12.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{how much \Nthe World Government messed up my life!-OG}do quanto o Governo Mundial\Narruinou minha vida!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:16.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you hate the government that much, \Nthen why are you helping them?!-OG}Se os odeia tanto,\Npor que está ajudando eles?!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I have a wish I want to come \Ntrue even if I have to give up everything.-OG}Porque não importa o custo,\Ntenho um desejo que preciso realizar.{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:34.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There're two conditions \Nthat CP9 forced on me in this town.-OG}Havia duas condições\Nque a CP9 me impôs nesta cidade.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{One is to pin \Nthe assassination on the Straw Hats.-OG}A primeira era colocar a culpa do assassinato\Nnos Chapéus de Palha.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:45.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The other is to turn myself \Nin to the government and obey them.-OG}A segunda era me entregar ao governo\Ne obedecer todas as suas ordens.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se fizer isso, você também vai morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:53.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why do you accept such conditions \Nafter evading them for 20 years?-OG}Depois de fugir por vinte anos,\Npor que aceitar um acordo desses agora?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In this lone instance,-OG}Nesta única ocasião,{WF+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:20:02.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{CP9 has been given permission to exercise buster call against the Straw Hats.-OG}a CP9 recebeu autorização para executar\Num buster call contra os Chapéus de Palha.{WF+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:03.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Buster call?-OG}Um buster call?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's an emergency order to summon five of the vice admirals from Marine Headquarters and ten battleships to one place.-OG}É uma chamada prioritária ao Quartel-General da Marinha{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:11.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's an emergency order to summon five of the vice admirals from Marine Headquarters and ten battleships to one place.-OG}para enviar cinco vice-almirantes\Ne dez navios de guerra a um local.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:16.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once you've been targeted by the national war-class military power-OG}Uma vez que seja alvo de tamanha\Nforça militar esmagadora,{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{nothing will remain of you.-OG}a chance de sobrevivência é absolutamente zero.{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:23.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Normally, in the Marines, this authority only belongs to the three admirals and the head of the Marines, the fleet admiral.-OG}Normalmente, essa autoridade pertence\Napenas aos três almirantes{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Normally, in the Marines, this authority only belongs to the three admirals and the head of the Marines, the fleet admiral.-OG}e ao almirante de frota\Nque lidera a Marinha.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas desta vez,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{through the admiral Aokiji,-OG}graças ao Almirante Aokiji,{WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 2000)}{CP9 was given the authority \Nto exercise it just this once.-OG}a CP9 foi autorizada a usá-lo apenas desta vez.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:41.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I didn't accept the conditions, \Nbuster call was going to be exercised on us.-OG}Se eu não tivesse cooperado,\Num buster call teria caído sobre nós.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:45.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When I heard the name Aokiji, I gave up.-OG}Assim que ouvi o nome Aokiji, desisti.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was always able to make good \Nmy escape for the past 20 years-OG}Nestes últimos vinte anos,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:53.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{because I had nothing to protect...-OG}nunca tive problema em fugir\Nporque não tinha nada a proteger...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I could betray people \Nand use them as a shield.-OG}Porque podia trair os outros\Ne usá-los como escudo.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But...-OG}Mas agora...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I really can't do that any longer.-OG}não posso simplesmente abandoná-los.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The life I once gave up on...-OG}A vida que um dia descartei...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O coração que perdi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:13.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The dream I could no longer have... \NThey picked them all up for me.-OG}Os sonhos que achei que tinham morrido...\NEles trouxeram todos de volta pra mim.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:16.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was able to make friends \Nwho would believe in someone like me.-OG}Encontrei amigos...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was able to make friends \Nwho would believe in someone like me.-OG}que realmente acreditam em mim.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{your wish is...-OG}qual é o seu desejo?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:32.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That the six Straw Hats, excluding me, \Ncan leave this island safely!-OG}{\q2}Que os seis piratas Chapéu de Palha, exceto eu,\Npossam deixar esta ilha em segurança!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you saying, for that, \Nyou don't care if the weapon is brought back?!-OG}Você reviveria a arma por {\i1}isso{\i0}?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:39.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se importa com o que acontece com o mundo?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right. I don't!-OG}Não me importo!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Enough of that nonsense!-OG}Chega dessa besteira!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:54.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não consegui puxar o gatilho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of all people,-OG}De todas as pessoas...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{over the lives of everyone in this world,-OG}Acima das vidas de todos neste mundo...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:09.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{she chose the lives of the six of you.-OG}Ela escolheu salvar vocês seis.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:12.23,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi por nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:17.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that I might have the weapon's \Nblueprints taken away by them,-OG}Agora que provavelmente vão roubar\Nas plantas da arma,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:19.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't have the right to criticize her, though.-OG}não tenho muito moral pra criticá-la, acho.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:27.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O que houve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:32.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good...-OG}Que alívio...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:35.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então a Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{didn't betray us after all.-OG}não nos traiu, afinal!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:44.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'd better gather everyone \Nimmediately and let them know! Thanks, Iceburg-san!-OG}{\q2}Preciso reunir todo mundo agora mesmo\Ne contar! Obrigada, Iceburg!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:47.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! Straw Hat and the others were beaten!-OG}Espera! Vocês todos apanharam feio!{CPS, WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:48.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you think you can do now?!-OG}O que acha que pode fazer agora?!{CPS, WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:52.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It starts now!-OG}{\i1}Começa{\i0} agora!{CPS, WF+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:56.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It starts now! Luffy and the others are fine. It'd take a lot more than that to take them out.-OG}O Luffy e os outros estão bem.\NVai precisar mais que isso pra derrubá-los.{CPS, WF+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna get Robin back!-OG}Vamos trazer a Robin de volta!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:01.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When unsure, anyone can be weak. - OG}As pessoas vacilam diante da incerteza.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:08.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no limit to their strength \Nwhen they know it's okay to save her! -OG}Quando souberem que ela precisa de ajuda,\Nnão vão parar até ela estar a salvo!{Gaijin/AR}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:14.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper! Acorda! Precisamos encontrar todo mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper! Ei, acorda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:22.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey, he's really \Nseriously injured, you know...-OG}– Ei, ei, ele está gravemente ferido...\N– Ei, ei, ele está gravemente ferido...{CPS, WF+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:25.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acorda! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:28.18,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:32.81,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You go join Luffy and the others \Nand tell them everything that just happened...-OG}Vai encontrar o Luffy e os outros\Ne conta tudo o que acabou de acontecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.94,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{without leaving a single word out.-OG}Não deixe de fora uma palavra sequer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.31,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you gonna do?-OG}E você?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.31,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos separar aqui por um tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.65,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, não se preocupe.\NEu não vou fazer nada imprudente.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:48.37,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.70,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder...-OG}Será que...{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.78,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{if Robin doesn't like us anymore.-OG}a Robin não gosta mais da gente?{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:56.79,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:01.21,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Remember one thing.-OG}Lembre de uma coisa:{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:05.63,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando uma mulher mente...{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.34,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,um verdadeiro homem perdoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:16.60,Main-207+,,0,0,22,,{For today's last service to Enies Lobby, departing at 11 PM,-OG}{\q2\i1}Para o último trem com destino a Enies Lobby, partindo às onze,{\i0}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:23.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}por favor embarquem pelo saguão do segundo andar\Ndevido ao nível elevado da água.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:25.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's go check them out!-OG}Ei, vamos dar uma espiada!{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:25.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:34.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since this involves a secret operation, you're forbidden to see them board.-OG}Como se trata de uma operação secreta,\Né proibido ver quem embarca.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:35.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, darn...-OG}– Droga!\N– Droga!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.04,0:24:46.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You were chased after for the past 20 years.-OG}Perseguimos você por vinte anos.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.05,0:24:48.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm surprised that you gave up now.-OG}Estou surpreso que finalmente desistiu.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.65,0:25:02.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bingo...-OG}Bingo.{WF}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=19}===============================DIALOGUE============================
